```
for(int i = 0; i &lt; n.length; i++) {
    count[n[i]]++;
    if(count[n[i]] &gt; maxCount) {
        maxCount = count[n[i]];
        val = n[i];
    }
}
```
To this:
```
// first do the counting
for(int i = 0; i &lt; n.length; i++) {
    count[n[i]]++;
}
// then find the one which appears the most
for(int i = 0; i &lt; n.length; i++) {
    if(count[n[i]] &gt; maxCount) {
        maxCount = count[n[i]];
        val = n[i];
    }
}
```

